			<h3>COVID-19 and Arkansas School Closings</h3>
				<p>Gov. Asa Hutchinson announced that the closure of on-site instruction for K-12 schools will be extended to the end of the school year based upon public health conditions. 
					Education will continue through alternative methods of instruction (AMI). Arkansas AMI, the partnership between DESE and Arkansas PBS, will be expanded with programming 
					through the end of the current school year. Viola will continue development of AMI content so that instruction of students can continue at home.<br></p>
<br><h3>2020 Senior Class Exit Form</h3>
				<p>Due to school being closed at this time, the Viola Public School District is making the 2020 Senior Class Exit form available as a PDF document for your convenience. All 
					senoirs must fill out this form and return it to Mrs. May or Mr. Ivens by May 8, 2020.<br>
				Click <a href="pdf/2020%20Senior%20Exit%20Form.pdf" target="blank">here</a> to download the form. 
					</p>
<br><h3>Kindergarten Registration Packet</h3>
